    "title": "UN envoy says Jeddah deal can still anchor future Sudan peace talks, as fears grow over El-Obeid",
    "description": "NEW YORK CITY: The 2023 Jeddah agreement brokered by Saudi Arabia can still serve as a foundation for future Sudan peace talks, the UN’s special envoy for Sudan, Pekka Haavisto, said on Thursday, even as he voiced alarm over an intensifying offensive by the Rapid Support Forces around the city of El-Obeid.",
